//! Sapiens Integration Layer
//!
//! Generated by backbone-schema. Do not edit manually.
//!
//! This module provides the Anti-Corruption Layer (ACL) for integrating
//! with other modules. All external module dependencies should go through
//! adapters defined here.
//!
//! ## Why Anti-Corruption Layer?
//!
//! - Isolates internal domain from external changes
//! - Translates external concepts to internal language
//! - Provides single point for external dependencies
//!
//! ## Usage
//!
//! ```text
//! use crate::integration::ExternalModuleAdapter;
//!
//! let adapter = ExternalModuleAdapter::new(external_service);
//! let internal_entity = adapter.translate_to_internal(external_dto)?;
//! ```

